# Testing & Deployment Rules

- Unit tests: minimum 80% coverage.
- Integration tests: all API endpoints tested with Supertest/Postman.
- End-to-end tests: simulate civilian, officer, and judge journeys with Cypress/Playwright.
- CI/CD pipeline must use GitHub Actions + Docker + Kubernetes.
